"{\"uid\": \"cityam.com-andy-murray-reveals-paris-2024-olympic-ambition-and-retirement-thinking\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Featured  Submit a story  Tell us your story.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 45, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Featured  Submit a story  Tell us your story.\", \"from\": 47, \"to\": 92, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Featured  Submit a story  Tell us your story.\", \"from\": 94, \"to\": 139, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"By:Frank Dalleres  Sports Editor  Andy Murray has declared that he wants one more shot at the Olympics in Paris this summer before his retirement from tennis.\", \"from\": 141, \"to\": 299, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 175, \"end\": 186, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.626572728751205e-47, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 247, \"end\": 252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999981314858082, \"rank\": 1.8685175977038191e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Briton rates hisLondon 2012 goldmedal the highlight of his career and successfully defended his men's singles title in Rio four years later.\", \"from\": 301, \"to\": 445, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 301, \"end\": 311, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Briton\", \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Briton\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q25379\", \"Q234460\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Briton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Briton\"}, {\"begin\": 424, \"end\": 427, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9993456212010396, \"rank\": 0.00065480728626399, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Competing for Team GB atParis 2024would be a fitting stage for the final act of a career Murray has admitted is in its final months.\", \"from\": 447, \"to\": 579, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 536, \"end\": 542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.236995193063267e-30, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's been brilliant experiences, especially in London and Rio, but I also learnt some great lessons from Beijing.\", \"from\": 581, \"to\": 695, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 629, \"end\": 635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9937496457756374, \"rank\": 0.006229957294351955, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 640, \"end\": 643, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9993456212010396, \"rank\": 0.00065480728626399, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 687, \"end\": 694, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999998931757602, \"rank\": 1.0680642473279707e-07, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hopefully I can get the chance to compete in another one,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 696, \"to\": 763, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I would say this because I have done well in the Olympics, but I also know how I felt when I lost in the first round in Beijing - that was a really harsh lesson for me.\", \"from\": 765, \"to\": 934, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 886, \"end\": 893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999998931757602, \"rank\": 1.0680642473279707e-07, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stay in the game with The Turnover: your weekly roundup of sport business news, expert analysis and behind\\u2011the\\u2011scenes stories from City\\u202fAM's sports desk.\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 1089, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was so excited to be part of an Olympic Games and I was really devastated by that because I [was] not going to get a chance to do this for another four years.\\\"\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1253, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray has not passed the third round of a Grand Slam since 2017 and in recent months has struggled to string together any kind of winning run.\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1398, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1255, \"end\": 1261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.236995193063267e-30, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 1304, \"end\": 1308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Slam_of_Curling\", \"score\": 0.9831549163878989, \"rank\": 0.0171337022592981, \"text\": \"Slam\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Slam_of_Curling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Slam_of_Curling\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 36-year-old has spoken aboutnearing the endof his playing days but has not decided how much notice he will give people once he decides on a retirement date.\", \"from\": 1400, \"to\": 1560, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is no right way of finishing your career and everyone is different so what might be the right way for [Roger] Federer might not be the right way for [Rafael] Nadal, might not be the right way for [Novak] Djokovic,\\\" he added to the BBC'sToday Programme.\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1821, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1773, \"end\": 1781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9967506536287215, \"rank\": 0.003259939042305573, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Pete Sampras won the US Open, did not say anything and did not play tennis again.\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1905, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1824, \"end\": 1836, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pete_Sampras\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pete Sampras\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pete_Sampras\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pete_Sampras\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Roger Federer finished his career playing a doubles match with Rafa Nadal.\", \"from\": 1906, \"to\": 1980, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1906, \"end\": 1919, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Federer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Roger Federer\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Federer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Federer\"}, {\"begin\": 1969, \"end\": 1979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rafa Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Who would have expected that?\", \"from\": 1981, \"to\": 2010, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I thought it was an amazing way to finish - his greatest rival being on the same side of the net as him was really special.\", \"from\": 2011, \"to\": 2138, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When the time is right I will probably say something before I play my last match and my last tournament.\", \"from\": 2140, \"to\": 2245, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Whether I say anything months ahead of time, I do not know.\\\"\", \"from\": 2246, \"to\": 2306, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Share this article  Subscribe to the City AM newsletter to have our top stories delivered directly to your inbox.\", \"from\": 2308, \"to\": 2421, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow us for breaking news and latest updates\", \"from\": 2423, \"to\": 2469, \"entities\": []}]}"